metadata.name: Executive Founders Pass
metadata.description:
Bubbleworld is an ecosystem of premium collections launching on the Bubblehouse NFT marketplace. From top NFL players like Leonard Fournette to Tik Tokers like Brooke Monk to the most amazing digital artists globally, Bubbleworld is a rich ecosystem of projects, where the Founders Passes are the VIPs in the ecosystem.

The Executive Founders Pass (EFP) is INVITE ONLY, limited to 300 editions, and only top founders, influencers, and Bubblehouse / Bubbleworld ecosystem whales are invited to hold one. The EFP is NOT allocated all at once, but rather invites are given out over time to those that Bubbleworld invites to mint.

The EFP gives 100% guaranteed VIP whitelist access to every exclusive Bubbleworld collection from PFP related projects to NBA players, fashion, influencers, hospitality, and more.

The EFP is the only pass that gives 0% platform commission on every collection, and 0% royalty on every Bubbleworld collection.

The EFP also grants access to the largest amount of Bubble tokens, staking rewards, access to exclusive Bubbleworld events, Diamond Chest + Mystery Box airdrops and more.

The EFP is also access to an exclusive community of top Web 3 players and whales in the Bubbleworld ecosystem.

See the deck for the full suite of Bubbleworld ecosystem: https://pitch.com/v/Bubbleworld-6hsehs
